start-0 = Welcome to the world of Rusted Ruins! You arrived in a legendary continent, and there are a lot of ruins.

    The first object is to visit near town, and prepare for your adventure. To enter a town, press "Enter" key in this region map.

    In a town, an informant will teach you the location of ruins. And you can buy many useful items from shopkeepers. You should prepare equipments and foods there before going into ruins.

    Ruins are dangerous because many monsters live there. Let's slay monsters and bring back a lot of valuable items.
